title: My Journey
author: canobiecrazy
pages:
#- 9-7-2013

Today I rode a horse to Commonwealth. I got an inventory fo stuff for our commune, and then took my saddle off of Equus and put it on an unnamed tan horse. I named her Butterscotch. It went well, I went via the Aurora trail. I got to 
#- a place called Nowhere, and I had to leave Butterscotch behind, but I took my saddle. I got there harm-free. I went about 12 kilometers.
#- 